      • scaleOut

        public void scaleOut(Tier tier,
                     double factor)
        Modify the number of replicas of the specified resource reducing it multiplying it by the provided factor and ceiling the result. If the resulting number of replicas is equal or lower than the original one (factor is <= 1) it falls back to the scaleOut function that adds just 1 replica
